  "title": "[Non-Patient Fronting] Office Hours Pharmacy Technician @ Clementi #HCY",
  "description": "<p>Working Hours: 5.25 Days office hours, alternate Saturday Half Day<br />Location: Clementi (Transport from Jurong East MRT)<br />Salary: $2200-$3300 (Based on experience)</p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>· Assist pharmacists in dispensing medications to patients.</p><p>· Accurately prepare and label prescriptions according to prescriptions or medication orders.</p><p>· Manage medication inventory, including stocking, organizing, and tracking medication supplies.</p><p>· Perform drug preparation duties, including measuring, counting, and mixing medications.</p><p>· Provide patient counseling under the supervision of the pharmacist on proper medication usage and side effects.</p><p>· Assist with maintaining pharmacy records and patient information.</p><p>· Ensure compliance with legal, regulatory, and safety requirements.</p><p>· Communicate with healthcare providers regarding prescription issues and medication clarifications.</p><p>· Handle customer service inquiries and ensure a positive patient experience.</p><p>· Manage prescription refills and process insurance claims.</p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>Diploma in Pharmaceutical Science or a related field.</p><p>For interested candidates, please send your most recent and updated resume to<strong>sallytsin</strong><a href=\"mailto:aliciacheong@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>WA me at <a href=\"http://wa.me/+6598326219\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://wa.me/+6598326219</a> or tele me at @sallytsin<br /><br /></p><p>Tsin Chien Yee Sally<br />R25127272<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />EA License No. 99C4599</p>",
